ass]] [[attack cargo ship]] that was sunk as an artificial reef off [[Myrtle Beach, South Carolina|Myrtle Beach]]. | |- |[[USS Weehawken (1862)|USS ''Weehawken'']] |6 December 1863 |[[American Civil War]] [[Monitor (warship)|monitor]] at Charleston. |{{Coord|32.7157|-79.8903|name=USS Weehawken (1862)}} |- |[[SS William Lawrence Shipwreck Site|SS ''William Lawrence'']] |February 1899 |A [[cargo ship]] that was wrecked in a storm off [[Hilton Head Island, SC|Hilton Head Island]]. | |}
